<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remind-vt">remind <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'maɪnd/    美 /rɪ'maɪnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>提醒</strong></h4>
<p>to make sb remember sth that they must do：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Remind you</strong>, Jane. Take care. My wife got her purse picked at the station once. 
提醒你一下，简，要当心。我妻子的钱包曾在火车站被偷过。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>remind sb about / of:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I forgot to remind him about / of the time for the interview. 
我忘了提醒他面试的时间。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>remind sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We put up a board to remind people to protect the trees.
我们竖起一块牌子提醒人们保护树木。</p><footer>2009 北京</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>remind sb + (that) / wh-从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She reminded me that I hadn’t called Mother.
她提醒我还没有给妈妈打电话。</p><footer>2011 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do something you’re good at. Remind yourself how good you are at so many things. 
做点你擅长的事，要提醒自己你是多么的多才多艺。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>使想起</strong></h4>
<p>to make sb remember sb that they know or sth that happened in the past：</p>
<ul>
<li>remind sb of sb / sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bill reminded him of the day years ago when they had first met. 
比尔使他想起多年前他们初识的那一天。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Brad was Jane’s brother! 
布拉德是简的兄弟。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— No wonder he reminded me so much of Jane!
难怪他让我觉得他那么像简呢。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>reminder /rɪ'maɪndə(r)/ n   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He placed the brochure on his desk as a reminder. 
他把手册放在桌上作为提醒。</p><footer>2011 山东</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The photo will remind me <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the days when we were together.  （2007 浙江改）  </li>
<li>In our childhood, we were often <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (提醒) by Grandma to pay attention to our table manners.  （2005 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. of  2. reminded  </p></div>